{"tid":1137134,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"作為香港人，我其實幾自豪。","createTime":"2019-05-03T13:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T13:59:25.000Z","uid":250247,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7f24dde284a21d8ed055f9e05650611d0988d00c","tid":1137134,"uid":250247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T13:50:51.000Z","msg":"係外國讀書 比人問邊度嚟<br />\nI&rsquo;m from Hong Kong<br />\n佢地就會話oh china<br />\n我會話Somewhere near China but not<br />\n上堂比professor 話我係Chinese<br />\n會同佢講HK is not China<br />\n我地有自己嘅貨幣 一國兩制<br />\n有個大陸人就話For me, HK is China.<br />\n落堂前個professor講哂sorry <br />\n話啲大陸人無知 叫我地唔好理佢<br />\n<br />\n就算香港宜家變成點<br />\n政制有幾唔好 <br />\n市民嘅素質有幾唔好（都係因為啲偽香港人姐）<br />\n我作為香港人 我真係幾自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd3bae946ffdb19fd9a6511055791622f21f680","tid":1137134,"uid":195904,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T13:59:25.000Z","msg":"我地同時係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好自豪呢個身份<br />\n特別08年嗰時見到祖國越來越強大 好光榮"}]}